---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Oktaviary Log">
  <div class="page">

    <header>
      <p class="back"><a href="/">Oktaviary Log</a></p>
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">

      <p>The log began as a need to record without explaining.</p>
      <p>Not to publish. Not to perform.</p>
      <p>Just to leave a trace.</p>

      <p class="divider">—</p>

      <p>This is a place for things that don't fully belong anywhere else.</p>
      <p>Writings. Mixes. Conversations. Fragments.</p>
      <p>Some of them connect.<br />Most of them don't.</p>
      <p>That's fine.</p>

      <p class="divider">—</p>

      <p>Identity here is left incomplete.</p>
      <p>What appears is not a person,<br />but a pattern.</p>
      <p>Something that repeats,<br />changes,<br />contradicts itself,<br />and continues anyway.</p>

      <p class="divider">—</p>

      <p>Oktaviary is just a name.</p>
      <p>The log is the real thing.</p>

      <p class="divider">—</p>

      <p>This is not building toward anything.</p>
      <p>No conclusion. No final version.</p>
      <p>Just entries.</p>
      <p>The log continues.</p>

    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .back {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .back a {
    color: #888;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back a:hover {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: normal;
  }

  .prose {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #2a2a2a;
  }

  .divider {
    color: #ccc;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>
